Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou There is always a hidden cost. Always ask yourself what's more expensive? Buying a healthy meal for $10 or paying a medical bill after having a stroke? Paying for a useful education once or dying full of regrets?'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou The most expensive things are not the ones with the biggest price tag. It's the things you don' do that come back to bite you. Want proof?'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Imagine you don't invest in learning how to make a million dollars. You might save yourself a few grand but every year you don't make a million.... You pay the difference for your ignorance. Here's an example:'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Let's say you make $50,000/ year. Every year you don't make a million, it's costing your $950,000 Because you could have made that- you just didn't know how to.'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou So be wise what opportunities you pass on- It might be the biggest regret of your life! Always invest in yourself!'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Now, look at your dreams and goals... And don't ask if you can ever afford them. Ask if you can afford NOT to Invest in yourself!'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou If your current lifestyle can't finance them... How will this ever change if you do nothing? So don' let your dreams die and wither just because you wanted to save a few dollars.'.

Photo shared by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021 tagging @basharjkatou. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Take action and do something about your goals NOW. w If you don't know how to start- follow my page @basharjkatou, it's gonna give you a few pointers on where to go. And now go get it!'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'ALLAROUNDBUSINESS JASON STATHAM SAID: I just want to work hard, make money, eat with good people and love the same woman over and over again. -Jason Statham'.
Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 6 people, beard, sunglasses and text that says 'FIRST THEY MAKE FUN OF YOU, ALLAROUNDBUSINESS THEN THEY COPY.'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'Lady Gaga took a photo with and gave money to a homeless man. When she leaned in for the photo, he said "I smell" to which she replied, "don't worry, smell too." ALLAROUNDBUSINESS ALLAROUNDE'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'ላ O m ALLAROUNDBUSINESS ROUNDBUSINESS DON'T TELL PEOPLE WHAT YOU'RE GOING TO DO. DO IT AND SHOCK THEM. AND AFTER SHOCKING THEM, STAY SILENT. MOVE ON TO YOUR NEXT PROJECT. KEEP SHOCKING, KEEP ENJOYING.'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'AL AROUND BUSINESS ALBERT EINSTEIN ONCE SAID: want If you to live a happy life, tie it to a goal, not to people or things.'.

Photo by Business | Motivation | Quotes on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'IF A CLIENT TELLS YOU: I KNOW PEOPLE THAT CHARGE LESS ALLAROUNDBUSINESS RESPOND: I GOT CLIENTS THAT PAY MORE Keep developing your skills to the level that allow you to work with whoever you want.'.
